---
import type { HomeSectionBaseProps } from './section-contract';

const { enabled, order } = Astro.props as HomeSectionBaseProps;
if (!enabled) return null;
---

<section
 style={`order:${order}`}
 class="bg-[#0D0A08] text-[#F5EDD6] border-y border-[rgba(184,115,51,0.14)]"
>
 <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
 <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 flex-wrap">
 <div>
 <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Uygulama Gibi Kullan</h2>
 <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[#c9b190]">
 Şanlıurfa rehberini ana ekrana ekleyin, hızlı açılışla uygulama deneyimi alın.
 </p>
 </div>
 <p class="rounded-sm border border-[rgba(184,115,51,0.18)] bg-[#1A1008]/70 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-medium text-[#e6d4b2]">
 Android için tarayıcı menüsündeki <strong class="text-white">Ana ekrana ekle</strong> seçeneğini kullanın.
 </p>
 </div>

 <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
 <article class="rounded-sm border border-[rgba(184,115,51,0.2)] bg-[#1A1008]/80 p-4">
 <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Android (Chrome)</h3>
 <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[#c9b190]">
 “Uygulamayı Yükle” butonuna tıklayın veya menüden “Ana ekrana ekle”.
 </p>
 <button
  type="button"
  data-pwa-install
  hidden
  class="mt-3 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-gradient-to-r from-[#C0571F] to-[#D49718] px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-white transition hover:opacity-90"
 >
  📱 Uygulamayı Yükle
 </button>
 </article>
 <article class="rounded-sm border border-[rgba(184,115,51,0.2)] bg-[#1A1008]/80 p-4">
 <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">iOS (Safari)</h3>
 <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[#c9b190]">
 Paylaş menüsünden “Ana Ekrana Ekle” ile uygulama gibi kullanın.
 </p>
 </article>
 </div>
 </div>
</section>
